    "description": "If you're a passionate Business Development Manager with drive and ambition, Sobha Developers Holdings Services in Gwalior is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Sobha Developers Holdings Services:\nSobha Developers Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Maintain a pipeline of qualified leads using CRM software\n• Prepare presentations and proposals for institutional clients\n• Coordinate with architects, contractors, and project teams\n• Negotiate pricing, terms, and conditions on behalf of clients\n• Conduct market research and provide competitive analysis\n• Manage relationships with existing customers post-purchase\n• Liaise with banks and NBFCs for home loan assistance to customers\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Property Valuation\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in Market Research\n• Proficiency in Title Search\n• Proficiency in Portfolio Management\n• Proficiency in Contract Management\n• Proficiency in Negotiation Skills\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Referral bonus program\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Gwalior, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Sobha Developers Holdings Services!",
